The paper discusses the intersection of symbolic computation and satisfiability checking, which falls under the category of cs.SC (Symbolic Computation). The paper also discusses the development of heuristics, which is a common topic in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposal and discussion of standards and benchmarks also relates to the field of logic (cs.LO) and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper mentions the algorithm Cylindrical Algebraic Decomposition, which is commonly used in computational geometry (cs.CG).
